            <div type="transcript" id="F619A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Did you ever stand in a<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Cavern's Mouth -</l>
                    <l>Widths out of the Sun - </l>
                    <l>And look - and shudder,<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 and block your breath - </l>
                    <l>And deem to be alone </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>In such a place, what<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 horror,</l>
                    <l>How Goblin it would be - </l>
                    <l>And fly, as 'twere pursuing<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 you?  </l>
                    <l>Then Loneliness - looks so - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Did you ever look in a<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Cannon's face - </l>
                    <l>Between whose Yellow eye -</l>
                    <l>And your's - the Judgment<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 intervened - </l>
                    <l>The Question of &quot;To die&quot; - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Extemporizing in your ear </l>
                    <l>As cool as Satyr's Drums - </l>
                    <l>If you remember, and were<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 saved</l>
                    <l>It's liker so - it seems - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
